0.0.6 Jan-18
  * Switched to just supporting binary devices (lights can be selected via drop down rather than typing a name)
  * Switched from cron to setInterval to simplify the code

0.0.5 15-Dec-18
  * An almost total re-write
  * Define active hours - lights don't go on outside this
  * Support for security sensors turning on lights

0.0.4 19-Nov-17
  * Correctly zeroing secs, millisecs for sunrise/sunset

0.0.3 19-Nov-17
  * Fixed scheduling of randomised and sunrise/sunset entries (zerod seconds, milliseconds)
  * Removed rescheduled when Presence changes from/to night/home
  * Tidied up logging output